@startuml C4-Context-ToolWeave
' C4 Level 1 - System Context Diagram
' ToolWeave: NL-to-REST API bridge via MCP

title ToolWeave - C4 Level 1: System Context

top to bottom direction

!include ./assets/C4.puml

' ── Actors ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
rectangle "==Developer / MCP Client\n\n<size:10>[Person]</size>\n\n<i>Uses an MCP-compatible\nclient (Claude Desktop, app)\nto issue natural-language\nAPI requests</i>" <<person>> as developer

rectangle "==API Owner\n\n<size:10>[Person]</size>\n\n<i>Uploads OpenAPI/Swagger\nspecs to bootstrap\nthe API catalog</i>" <<person>> as api_owner

' ── Internal System ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
rectangle "==ToolWeave\n\n<size:10>[Software System]</size>\n\n<i>FastMCP server that\ntranslates natural-language\nprompts into REST API calls\nwith proposal gating\nfor write operations</i>" <<system>> as toolweave

' ── External Systems ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
rectangle "==Target REST APIs\n\n<size:10>[External Software System]</size>\n\n<i>Customer / partner REST\nservices that ToolWeave\nexecutes on behalf\nof the caller</i>" <<external_system>> as target_api

rectangle "==Amazon Bedrock\n\n<size:10>[External Software System]</size>\n\n<i>Claude 3 Haiku via\nConverse API for AI\nplanning and endpoint\nenrichment</i>" <<external_system>> as bedrock

rectangle "==DataDictionary MCP\n\n<size:10>[External Software System]</size>\n\n<i>Shared Lambda service\nthat provides field-level\nmetadata (format, constraints)</i>" <<external_system>> as data_dictionary

rectangle "==mcp-observatory\n\n<size:10>[External Software System]</size>\n\n<i>Risk scoring, HMAC\nproposal / commit tokens\nand invocation metrics</i>" <<external_system>> as observatory

' ── Relationships ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
developer --> toolweave : "Calls MCP tools\n[MCP over HTTPS]"
api_owner --> toolweave : "Uploads OpenAPI spec\ntriggers catalog ingestion\n[AWS Console / CLI]"
toolweave --> target_api : "Executes REST calls\non behalf of developer\n[HTTPS / JSON]"
toolweave --> bedrock : "AI planning\nand enrichment\n[AWS SDK / Converse API]"
toolweave --> data_dictionary : "Fetches field metadata\n[HTTP JSON-RPC]"
toolweave --> observatory : "Risk scoring, proposal\nand commit gating\n[Library in-process]"

@enduml
